name: Midnight Asia: Eat · Dance · Dream
overview: Night brings out the most playful side of Asia's metropolises. This docuseries captures the food, drink, music — and night owls who shine in the dark.

episodes.name: Tokyo, Japan
episodes.overview: Night falls and adventure calls in neon-swept, sprawling Tokyo for an 85-year-old club DJ, a traveling bartender and playful fetish partygoers.

episodes.name: Seoul, South Korea
episodes.overview: Rapid change makes for dynamic nightlife in Seoul as soulful fried chicken and local rice wine reign, and indie rockers get inspired by pansori folk.

episodes.name: Mumbai, India
episodes.overview: Manic. Magic. Mumbai's infectious hustle inspires a mixologist to set a high bar while an MC moves area rap forward and a buttery-snack seller dazzles.

episodes.name: Bangkok, Thailand
episodes.overview: Creativity bursts from all corners of chaotic Bangkok — be it a hidden gem, a stall of famed skewers, a superhero folk theater or an underground club.

episodes.name: Taipei, Taiwan
episodes.overview: Come as you are in "Asia's best-kept secret," where a night market serves Michelin-worthy oyster omelets and a red-hot spot spreads the joy of drag.
